title: Silicone Spatula Set, 6PCS Food Grade Mixing Spatulas Heat Resistant Rubber Scraper Spatulas for Baking, Cooking, and Mixing, Non-Stick and Dishwasher Safe (Pink)
features: PREMIUM QUALITY MATERIAL: Silicone spatula is made of food-grade silicone, BPA free, non-stick surface, can withstand high temperature up to 446°F (230°C), will never decompose any toxic substances, don't worry about melting or warping.

ONE-PIECE DESIGN: The one-piece seamless design won't trap food particles. Ergonomic handle is very easy to grip! Whether you are cooking, baking, garnishing or stirring, the spoon spatula works well.

CONVENIENT AND PRACTICAL: All spatulas are designed with a hanging loop for easy carrying and storage. It can also be hung up after cleaning to make it dry quickly. Easy to clean up and ensure food safety.
EASY TO CLEAN: After each use, simply wipe with water or place in the dishwasher to easily clean and remove excess grease and food.

PACKAGE INCLUDES:Silicone kitchen set contains 5 different sizes of silicone spoons spatulas and a silicone grease brush. It can meet your daily needs such as cooking and making bread biscuits in the kitchen and outdoor barbecue.
